{"tid":1126342,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[物理問題]點解冷氣導致全球暖化 唔係能量守恆嘅咩？？？","createTime":"2019-04-26T10:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T14:36:57.000Z","uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":75,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"48c09e58c82cbdcd11b1989fb71c0d1e86597fa0","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"冷氣係只係將室內入面嘅熱能排出室外，而入面涼左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但你熄左冷氣之後 外界都會同室內慢慢平衡翻。撇除冷氣平身consume 嘅energy, 佢大部份排出嘅熱都係源自室內，喺無額外能量釋出嘅時候 點解會造成全球暖氣化呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c115e65f8e054dc5c4ca1f79e31d24957b90f405","tid":1126342,"uid":213460,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"冷氣用好多好多電，電係燒化石燃料來嘅，全球暖化係因為燒化石燃料<br />\n利:9吹"},{"pid":"b31bbd2f4399fae4073e27db6a7a0e73d30b9522","tid":1126342,"uid":9315,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"c115e65f8e054dc5c4ca1f79e31d24957b90f405","tid":1126342,"uid":213460,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"冷氣用好多好多電，電係燒化石燃料來嘅，全球暖化係因為燒化石燃料<br />\n利:9吹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"因為trap住左太陽D熱囉  太陽D熱係外來  根本唔關地球D能量守恆事<br />\n<br />\n點解咁on9都有人問  更on9係咁都答錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0257451f1812426fb369376eb1ed47d15b0700a1","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":2,"dislike":30,"score":-28,"quote":{"pid":"b31bbd2f4399fae4073e27db6a7a0e73d30b9522","tid":1126342,"uid":9315,"like":37,"dislike":5,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"c115e65f8e054dc5c4ca1f79e31d24957b90f405","tid":1126342,"uid":213460,"like