,"dislike":5,"score":32,"quote":{"pid":"c115e65f8e054dc5c4ca1f79e31d24957b90f405","tid":1126342,"uid":213460,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"冷氣用好多好多電，電係燒化石燃料來嘅，全球暖化係因為燒化石燃料<br />\n利:9吹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:27:23.000Z","msg":"因為trap住左太陽D熱囉  太陽D熱係外來  根本唔關地球D能量守恆事<br />\n<br />\n點解咁on9都有人問  更on9係咁都答錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:30:33.000Z","msg":"冷氣點樣trap 住太陽啲熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"其實佢唔算錯<br />\n因為氣候暖化兩極啲冰就會少咗(溶晒變水<br />\n冰少咗太陽光反射少咗(正常係反射去返太空)<br />\n水多咗都會keep更多熱(水吸熱快<br />\n所以地球就會熱咗<br />\n<br />\n其實能量守恆唔係100%<br />\n跌粒殞石落地球已經多咗<br />\n除非你扔返上去太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa65c0af63e5234d0319d0858859a4aea8edcce","tid":1126342,"uid":37869,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:45:02.000Z","msg":"冷氣機要用電<br />\n電由燃燒化石燃料產生<br />\n燃燒化石燃料時會產生二氧化碳<br />\n二氧化氧係溫室氣體<br />\n溫室氣體會困住由太陽傳送到地球的能量<br />\n地球的能量就會越來越多 越來越熱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n金星的大氣層超過96%都係二氧化碳<br />\n所以金星好熱<br />\n比更接近太陽的水星熱"},{"pid":"bcfda4d5b8aac0bb345a0006c53dbf9bcd8fc0e2","tid":1126342,"uid":187753,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:45:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因為冷氣機既轉換率唔係100％當中有好多能量變左做熱力而非冷氣，導致輸入唔等於輸出，所以地球就熱左<br />\n利申：物理讀到中三就無讀"},{"pid":"8b273ccf14531ee52d1c584b87c4bd63b537b5e0","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"大家意思即係地球暖化唔係因為冷氣抽走室內能量，排放到出面導致，而係發電過程中放熱 唔關冷氣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d625baf08afd0ffd7e661b8b6cbe397f62f2d76","tid":1126342,"uid":111616,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:50:25.000Z","msg":"Law of thermodynamics, wiki states the logic about energy conservation in details."},{"pid":"3d1f85161432d7fc70e5471b44c7a82c48d4f7aa","tid":1126342,"uid":34241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"中學都有教<br />\nhigh energy region to low energy region 係自然發生<br />\n反其道就要有work done"},{"pid":"3b5a243bc9902c6d1be0cf6d2b4222f7559464b0","tid":1126342,"uid":59848,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"你包埋外太空嚟計咪守恆囉"},{"pid":"4648f1823a8f23a1b2885fedff0e994efa28a1bf","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b273ccf14531ee52d1c584b87c4bd63b537b5e0","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:50:23.000Z","msg":"大家意思即係地球暖化唔係因為冷氣抽走室內能量，排放到出面導致，而係發電過程中放熱 唔關冷氣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"咁諗ok?"},{"pid":"19e88225732304c1d11e637681647efcd0f9c7c2","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1f85161432d7fc70e5471b44c7a82c48d4f7aa","tid":1126342,"uid":34241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"中學都有教<br />\nhigh energy region to low energy region 係自然發生<br />\n反其道就要有work done"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"大家意思即係地球暖化唔係因為冷氣抽走室內能量，排放到出面導致，而係發電過程中放熱 唔關冷氣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c07182770a9f91ef34b1fde1336544d48cbb1ad6","tid":1126342,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"19e88225732304c1d11e637681647efcd0f9c7c2","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3d1f85161432d7fc70e5471b44c7a82c48d4f7aa","tid":1126342,"uid":34241,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:20:21.000Z","msg":"中學都有教<br />\nhigh energy region to low energy region 係自然發生<br />\n反其道就要有work done"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:33:29.000Z","msg":"大家意思即係地球暖化唔係因為冷氣抽走室內能量，排放到出面導致，而係發電過程中放熱 唔關冷氣事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"可以咁講<br />\n但係局部地區變得好熱就肯定關事<br />\n因為你抽哂d冷氣入室內<br />\n放哂d熱出室外<br />\n咁室外咪好熱"},{"pid":"d383e82eee24f4adeac4ef1918469df4157441bb","tid":1126342,"uid":64716,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"7128c6abaabea45103575ef0f9fe4eb1e07b3a5e","tid":1126342,"uid":224561,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T10:32:48.000Z","msg":"因為啲能量本身儲存喺第二樣嘢到(液/固/氣體)<br />\n你放晒佢地出嚟<br />\n就打破咗個平衡<br />\n而且會越嚟越快<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就好似一粒飯係冇用<br />\n但你食完就會畀到能量你<br />\n燒燃料就係消化過程<br />\n而屎就係附加物(廢氣如Co2)"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T11:41:20.000Z","msg":"其實係環保撚偷换概念。<br />\n簡單說，一個電發熱暖爐所消耗o既能量遠比冷氣高，但冇人會嘈，因為唔冷唔會用。<br />\n但冷氣就把室內熱度轉到室外，越密集散熱越慢，對室外o既人唔多唔少有影響。但同環保了無關係。<br />\n<br />\n樓主講得好中， 冷氣(inverter制熱)  其實除左本身energy消耗外，冷熱交换係一比一循環的。沒有其他轉化，e. g. co2 排放。<br />\n如果硬要針對power consumption黎講只係發電方案問題，假設全大陽能及風力發電，根本就冇野好講。<br />\n<br />\n環保撚智識有限但又想搶佔道德高地就係咁搬龍門。 簡單點講，佢地論點就係因為用電唔環保，所以最好唔用電<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de11df0b1ba31cbecac6579e45e58c560b1aa6f7","tid":1126342,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d383e82eee24f4adeac4ef1918469df4157441bb","tid":1126342,"uid":64716,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"7128c6abaabea45103575ef0f9fe4eb1e07b3a5e","tid":1126342,"uid":224561,"like":11,"dis